        "Description": "I had planned a concert tour\r\nby boat, but as soon as we got\r\nthe instruments loaded up and\r\nshipped off, a Shogun Ceanataur\r\nappeared to block our sea route.\r\nIf you could hunt it, that\u0027d be\r\nmusic to my ears!",
